15:13.045 --> 15:15.309
Come on, I can't stand
watching my delusional friend

15:15.447 --> 15:17.210
waste another precious Halloween.

15:17.316 --> 15:19.477
Ted, the slutty pumpkin is not coming.

15:19.585 --> 15:20.916
She might.

15:21.186 --> 15:23.347
Come on, Barney,
this is not about the odds.

15:23.455 --> 15:24.479
It's about believing.

15:24.590 --> 15:27.115
This girl, she represents something to me.

15:27.226 --> 15:29.194
I don't know, hope.

15:31.030 --> 15:32.054
Wow.

15:32.865 --> 15:35.629
