18:03.982 --> 18:05.074
Nice.

18:05.451 --> 18:08.045
Come on, Ted. Victoria's Secret party.
Now. Let's go.

18:08.620 --> 18:11.680
- I'm staying.
- Fine. Fine.

18:12.691 --> 18:13.783
What are you doing?

18:13.892 --> 18:15.723
I'm flippering you off.

18:20.499 --> 18:22.057
Sweetie, I'm so sorry.

18:22.167 --> 18:23.395
Seriously, it's not a big deal.

18:23.502 --> 18:26.960
He wanted to be a "we"
and I wanted to be an "I."

18:27.439 --> 18:29.304
Dudes are such chicks.

18:31.343 --> 18:33.072
